### Update contact (replace {{id}} with actual contact ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jonathan",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jonathan.doe@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Red",
  "birthday": "1990-01-15"
}

### Delete contact (replace {{id}} with actual contact ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/{{id}}